<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إتْيَانُ الْجِمَارِ مَاشِيَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(م د جة)</span> , قَالَ جَابِرٌ - رضي الله عنه - فِي صِفَةِ حَجِّهِ - صلى اللهُ عليه وسلَّم -: (<span class="c1">" فَرَمَاهَا) <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(مِنْ بَطْنِ الْوَادِي)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(بِسَبْعِ حَصَيَاتٍ)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">(مِثْلِ حَصَى الْخَذْفِ)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> (يَرْمِي عَلَى رَاحِلَتِهِ "</span>) <span class="c2">(٥)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
